thread.title_full: Someone On eBay Was Crazy Enough To Bid $99,900 On A Cheeto That Looks Like Harambe

author: Brandon Wenerd
title: Someone On eBay Was Crazy Enough To Bid $99,900 On A Cheeto That Looks Like Harambe
text:
Harambe was more than just a gorilla. He was a sweet prince. He was a a blessed savior to humanity. He died so that our memes can live. We will never forget him and miss him every day.
Someone over on eBay opened up a bag of Flamin’ Hot Cheetos and made a startling discovery: They found a Cheeto with a striking resemblance to Harambe the Gorilla. Over a 100 people have bid on it, including someone who bid $99,900.
Fingers crossed it’s Martin Shkreli
